gonna do about it? Huh?

25:42.279 --> 25:43.193
-Hey!
-What are you gonna do?

25:43.193 --> 25:45.500
All right, okay.

25:45.500 --> 25:47.763
Take him upstairs before he
starts shooting up the place.

25:51.637 --> 25:53.595
-No, no, no, no!
-Hey, hey, hey! That's enough.

25:53.595 --> 25:55.336
That's enough!
Now, ease up!

25:57.599 --> 25:59.427
You okay?

25:59.427 --> 26:01.037
Hey, you okay?

26:05.128 --> 26:09.524
Yeah, I'm sorry. I, um

26:09.524 --> 26:11.265
