26:39.772 --> 26:43.079
You stay the fuck
outta my sight.

26:52.175 --> 26:53.786
Now, close the window, quick.

27:01.663 --> 27:05.493
See?
Just the two of us.

27:05.493 --> 27:07.147
Just the two of us.

27:10.454 --> 27:12.456
My handsome boy.

27:12.456 --> 27:15.459
Your hands are so warm.

27:15.459 --> 27:17.113
Did you think
they would be cold?

27:20.508 --> 27:21.901
Kiss me.

27:39.353 --> 27:47.274
♪

28:00.374 --> 28:01.331
What?

28:03.420 --> 28:05.292
Dinner's ready.

28:05.292 --> 28:07.773
I'm not hungry.

28:07.773 --> 28:09.339
You've been staring
at that book

28:09.339 --> 28:10.819
for a day and a half,
maybe you should

28:10.819 --> 28:12.516
Just fuck off.
Just fuck off.

28:12.516 --> 28:13.474
You know what, Jade?

28:17.217 --> 28:18.435
Okay! Okay! Okay! Okay!

28:18.435 --> 28:21.612
I'm coming! Jesus!

28:21.612 --> 28:25.268
Uh, I wouldn't take too long
if I were you.

28:38.934 --> 28:40.719
You know, you should really
work on your party face.

28:43.025 --> 28:45.027
What are you doing,
sitting here all by yourself?

28:47.247 --> 28:50.293
