to give you, too.

30:11.766 --> 30:14.595
Excuse me.

30:14.595 --> 30:16.118
That was nice of you.

30:18.294 --> 30:22.081
Everybody needs a little
pick-me-up sometimes.

30:23.386 --> 30:26.302
