30:52.067 --> 30:54.374
Do you think...

30:55.810 --> 30:57.507
Could I kiss you?

30:58.857 --> 31:00.771
Oh, um, Julie...

31:00.771 --> 31:03.513
No. I was I was just kidding.
I didn't mean

31:03.513 --> 31:04.863
No, sweetie

31:04.863 --> 31:06.255
No, you know what?
Just forget it.

31:11.217 --> 31:14.394
So, this girl tells you she's
hearing voices and you just

31:14.394 --> 31:17.179
Look, I was skeptical.
Just like you, okay?

31:18.702 --> 31:21.923
But then...

31:21.923 --> 31:24.404
she showed me this.

31:24.404 --> 31:26.145
Look at that.

31:27.320 --> 31:28.625
That's the logo

31:28.625 --> 31:29.844
I know what it is.

31:29.844 --> 31:31.759
That was almost
three years ago.

31:31.759 --> 31:34.675
