-That's it. Yeah.

33:36.014 --> 33:37.711
Yup.

33:37.711 --> 33:40.496
-Oof!
-Little bit harder?

33:43.238 --> 33:46.894
Why don't you take a break?
Go sit with Ethan for a bit.

33:46.894 --> 33:49.070
I'll take over here.

33:49.070 --> 33:52.682
Are you stuck on your antenna?

33:52.682 --> 33:53.901
Yeah.

33:53.901 --> 33:55.337
Ow. Go slow, please.

33:55.337 --> 33:56.512
