35:51.018 --> 35:53.194
Can I come in?

35:53.194 --> 35:54.891
I'd rather you didn't.

35:54.891 --> 35:57.155
Please?

35:57.155 --> 35:59.679
This is the only place
in this house I can be alone.

35:59.679 --> 36:01.159
Well, sort of.

36:03.422 --> 36:05.163
-You look sad.
-Can I just come in?

36:05.163 --> 36:06.816
I'm having a really bad night.

36:13.040 --> 36:16.130
Are you going somewhere?
It looks like you're packing.

36:16.130 --> 36:19.829
No, I'm just...

36:19.829 --> 36:21.831
No.
It's hard to explain.

36:24.182 --> 36:25.748
