and that it was special.

36:52.645 --> 36:54.168
Why?

36:54.168 --> 36:57.171
You've been here
the longest out of anyone.

36:57.171 --> 36:59.913
Do you know what this place is?

37:09.314 --> 37:12.273
Seriously, man, I don't know why
you keep staring at that thing.

37:12.273 --> 37:13.927
I'm sorry. Hold on.

37:15.929 --> 37:18.497
This page, it's...

37:19.759 --> 37:21.804
What?

37:21.804 --> 37:24.242
There's two pages
stuck together here.

37:33.947 --> 37:35.905
Whoa, whoa, whoa. Okay.

37:35.905 --> 37:38.081
Huh.

37:38.081 --> 37:39.909
