38:29.829 --> 38:31.265
Hi, Trudy.

38:31.265 --> 38:33.136
How how do you know my name?

38:33.136 --> 38:35.051
We know all your names.

38:50.023 --> 38:51.807
I'm just saying...

38:54.027 --> 38:57.944
I've been here longer than
him. Deserve a little respect.

39:01.295 --> 39:03.166
I could really help this
place if they just

39:03.166 --> 39:05.995
What the...?

39:05.995 --> 39:07.083
Is that blood?

39:07.083 --> 39:09.999
Jeez...

39:09.999 --> 39:11.610
What the...?

39:15.004 --> 39:16.876
Ah!

39:18.530 --> 39:21.794
