40:07.361 --> 40:11.017
You go first.

40:11.017 --> 40:13.149
I'll follow you down.

40:13.149 --> 40:15.413
Here. Take this.

40:22.942 --> 40:23.986
You ready?

40:39.262 --> 40:41.047
Follow protocol!

40:41.047 --> 40:44.267
Find your buddy!
Get into the van! Come on!

40:44.267 --> 40:46.269
Wait, Donna!
What are you doing?

40:46.269 --> 40:48.533
-Where's Ellis and Julie?
-I don't know.

40:48.533 --> 40:50.186
-Hey, Donna!
-I am not running.

40:50.186 --> 40:51.449
Okay. You've gotta get
those people to town.

40:51.449 --> 40:52.972
Save as many as you can.

40:52.972 --> 40:54.190
-Follow protocol.
-Okay, okay.

40:56.584 --> 40:58.238
All right, everyone.
Out of the way.

40:58.238 --> 40:59.848
Get in the van!

41:07.334 --> 41:10.250
Oh, my God.

41:11.512 --> 41:13.209
Oh, my God. Hurry up!

