43:54.066 --> 43:55.720
Please!

43:55.720 --> 43:57.504
Please, please, please, please!
Please. Please...

43:58.897 --> 44:00.463
Don't be like that.

44:00.463 --> 44:03.379
We were having
so much fun.

44:38.153 --> 44:40.373
How'd you know
that was gonna work?

44:40.373 --> 44:41.461
I didn't.

44:44.464 --> 44:46.074
With your dad
and the RV I just

