-Please, no.
-Okay, it's okay.

47:19.924 --> 47:21.708
-Please!
-Let me stop the bleeding!

47:21.708 --> 47:23.492
Please... No.

47:23.492 --> 47:24.711
-You're okay.
-No.

47:24.711 --> 47:26.539
-You're okay.
-No...

47:26.539 --> 47:29.411
You're okay.
You are okay.

47:29.411 --> 47:31.500
